{"tid":1542683,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"其實吹夠啲陰謀論風未","createTime":"2019-09-05T02:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:42:24.000Z","uid":41744,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2049a791069b817c2a5cb533707aec8d3f62cbe8","tid":1542683,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"個個都過份解讀<br />\n同蘋果煙花廣告一撚樣<br />\n唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問心 <br />\n打死人 要封鎖事件<br />\n現今香港社會根本冇可能<br />\n你話發生係大陸我都信<br />\n但香港仲係香港 未完全同化晒<br />\n要掩口涉及大量人 我唔信冇一個會收晒錢<br />\n亦唔信唔收錢個堆會搵唔到方法講件事出黎<br />\n隔離美國議員POST又係 又講咩CID收風好勁乜乜乜<br />\n屌唔講以為一堆藍屍係度9up<br />\n然後又一堆未經證實既對話圖 就撚晒你地<br />\n呢堆陰謀論我唔知係想轉移大家視線定點<br />\nCCTV係要拎 大家亦都可以呼籲知情人士出黎講<br />\n但唔好個個推爆晒啲未知真假 乜料都冇既POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"ce6dc45a3e177d39fb78c2fbabc835066ccf4dcf","tid":1542683,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:32:21.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7L